Geant9.6.p03 application SD

Detector geometry: world volume = cylinder (10 m diameter, 11 m height) of water; veto = sphere (4 m diameter) of scintillator (psuedocumene).

Scoring: veto = sensitive volume.

Hit info: track id, kinetic energy, position, time, volume name.

Retrieves info on hits and dumps result to screen.


